### MCP Noob Tutor - HTTP Test Requests
### Use REST Client extension to run these requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Explain Concept - HTTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toolName": "explain_concept",
  "input": {
    "concept": "HTTP"
  }
}

### Explain Concept - HTTP (with learner context - beginner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toolName": "explain_concept",
  "input": {
    "concept": "HTTP"
  },
  "userContext": {
    "learnerLevel": "beginner",
    "previousTopics": ["networks", "protocols"]
  }
}

